\c 11
\s Abahlali beJerusalema
\p
\v 1 Ngakho ababusi babantu bahlala eJerusalema\x + 1 Lan. 9.3.\x*; abantu abaseleyo basebesenza inkatho yokuphosa ukuze balethe oyedwa kwabalitshumi ukuhlala eJerusalema\x + 10.34. Hlu. 20.9. So 1 Lan. 24.31.\x* umuzi ongcwele\x + 11.18. Isa. 48.2. 52.1. Mat. 4.5. 27.53. Isam. 11.2. 21.2.\x*, lengxenye eziyisificamunwemunye \add kweminye\add* imizi.
\v 2 Abantu basebebusisa wonke amadoda azinikela ngesihle uku\add ya\add*hlala eJerusalema\x + Hlu. 5.2.\x*.
\p
\v 3 Lezi-ke zinhloko zesabelo ezahlala eJerusalema. Kodwa emizini yakoJuda bahlala, ngulowo kumfuyo yakhe, emizini yabo: UIsrayeli, abapristi, lamaLevi, lamaNethini\x + 1 Lan. 9.2.\x*, labantwana benceku zikaSolomoni\x + Ezra 2.55.\x*.
\v 4 EJerusalema\x + 1 Lan. 9.3.\x* kwahlala-ke \add abanye\add* babantwana bakoJuda lababantwana bakoBhenjamini. Ebantwaneni bakoJuda: OAthaya indodana kaUziya indodana kaZekhariya indodana kaAmariya indodana kaShefathiya indodana kaMahalaleli, owabantwana bakoPerezi,
\v 5 loMahaseya indodana kaBharukhi\x + 8.4.\x* indodana kaKolihoze\x + 3.15.\x* indodana kaHazaya indodana kaAdaya indodana kaJoyaribi indodana kaZekhariya indodana kaShiloni\x + 1 Lan. 9.5.\x*.
\v 6 Wonke amadodana kaPerezi ayehlala eJerusalema ayengamakhulu amane lamatshumi ayisithupha lesificaminwembili, amadoda alamandla.
\v 7 Lala ngamadodana kaBhenjamini: USalu indodana kaMeshulamu indodana kaJowedi indodana kaPhedaya indodana kaKolaya indodana kaMahaseya indodana kaIthiyeli indodana kaJeshaya\x + 1 Lan. 9.7.\x*,
\v 8 langemva kwakhe oGabayi, uSalayi, amakhulu ayisificamunwemunye lamatshumi amabili lesificaminwembili\x + 1 Lan. 9.9.\x*.
\v 9 LoJoweli indodana kaZikiri wayengumboni phezu kwabo, loJuda indodana kaHasenuwa engowesibili phezu komuzi.
\v 10 Kubapristi\x + 1 Lan. 9.10-13.\x*: OJedaya\x + Ezra 2.36.\x* indodana kaJoyaribi, uJakini\x + 1 Lan. 9.10.\x*,
\v 11 uSeraya indodana kaHilikhiya indodana kaMeshulamu indodana kaZadoki indodana kaMerayothi indodana kaAhitubi, umphathi wendlu kaNkulunkulu\x + 10.2. 1 Lan. 9.11.\x*,
\v 12 labafowabo ababesenza umsebenzi wendlu babengamakhulu ayisificaminwembili lamatshumi amabili lambili; loAdaya indodana kaJerohamu\x + Ezra 10.29,39. 1 Lan. 9.12.\x* indodana kaPelaliya indodana kaAmzi indodana kaZekhariya indodana kaPashuri indodana kaMalikiya\x + Ezra 2.38.\x*,
\v 13 labafowabo, inhloko zaboyise, babengamakhulu amabili lamatshumi amane lambili; loAmashayi indodana kaAzareli indodana kaAhizayi indodana kaMeshilemothi indodana kaImeri\x + 1 Lan. 9.12.\x*,
\v 14 labafowabo, amaqhawe alamandla, ikhulu lamatshumi amabili lesificaminwembili; lomboni phezu kwabo wayenguZabidiyeli indodana y\add omunye\add* wabakhulu.
\v 15 LakumaLevi\x + 1 Lan. 9.14-17.\x*: OShemaya indodana kaHashubi indodana kaAzirikamu indodana kaHashabhiya indodana kaBuni\x + 3.23.\x*;
\v 16 loShabethayi\x + Ezra 10.15.\x* loJozabadi\x + Ezra 8.33.\x* bezinhloko zamaLevi babephezu komsebenzi wangaphandle kwendlu kaNkulunkulu\x + 11.12. 1 Lan. 26.29.\x*;
\v 17 loMathaniya\x + 12.8,9,25. 11.22. 12.35. 1 Lan. 9.15.\x* indodana kaMika\x + 12.8,9,25. 11.22. 12.35. 1 Lan. 9.15.\x* indodana kaZabidi\x + 11.22. 10.11. 12.35.\x* indodana kaAsafi owayeyinhloko yokuqalisa ukubonga emkhulekweni\x + 12.8,24.\x*; loBakibukiya owesibili kubafowabo\x + 12.8,9,25. 11.22. 12.35. 1 Lan. 9.15.\x*; loAbida indodana kaShamuwa\x + 1 Lan. 9.16.\x*\x + 12.8,9,25. 11.22. 12.35. 1 Lan. 9.15.\x* indodana kaGalali indodana kaJeduthuni.
\v 18 Wonke amaLevi emzini ongcwele ayengamakhulu amabili lamatshumi ayisificaminwembili lane\x + 11.1.\x*.
\v 19 Labalindimasango, oAkubi, uTalimoni, labafowabo ababelinda amasango babelikhulu lamatshumi ayisikhombisa lambili.
\p
\v 20 Lensali yakoIsrayeli, ababapristi, amaLevi, babesemizini yonke yakoJuda, ngulowo elifeni lakhe\x + 11.3.\x*.
\v 21 LamaNethini ayehlala eOfeli\x + 1 Lan. 9.2.\x*; loZiha loGishipa babephezu kwamaNethini\x + Ezra 2.43.\x*.
\v 22 Njalo umboni wamaLevi eJerusalema wayenguUzi indodana kaBani\x + Ezra 2.10.\x* indodana kaHashabhiya indodana kaMathaniya\x + 11.17.\x* indodana kaMika\x + 11.17.\x*. Owamadodana kaAsafi, abahlabeleli babeqondene lomsebenzi wendlu kaNkulunkulu.
\v 23 Ngoba kwakungumlayo wenkosi ngabo\x + Ezra 6.8,9. 7.20.\x*, njengokufunekayo kubahlabeleli, udaba losuku ngosuku lwalo\x + 12.47. 2 Lan. 31.16.\x*.
\v 24 Njalo uPethahiya indodana kaMeshezabeli\x + 10.21. 3.4.\x*, owabantwana bakoZera indodana kaJuda, wayesesandleni senkosi kulo lonke udaba lwabantu\x + 1 Lan. 18.17. 23.28.\x*.
\v 25 Lemizaneni lamasimu ayo, kwahlala \add abanye\add* babantwana bakoJuda eKiriyathi-Arba\x + Josh. 21.11.\x* lemizana yayo\x + Nani 21.25.\x*, laseDiboni\x + Josh. 15.22.\x* lemizana yayo\x + Nani 21.25.\x*, laseJekabiseyeli lemizana yayo\x + Josh. 15.21.\x*,
\v 26 laseJeshuwa, laseMolada\x + Josh. 15.26,27,28.\x*, laseBeti-Peleti\x + Josh. 15.26,27,28.\x*,
\v 27 laseHazari-Shuwali\x + Josh. 15.26,27,28.\x*, laseBherishebha\x + Josh. 15.26,27,28.\x* lemizana yayo\x + Nani 21.25.\x*,
\v 28 laseZikilagi\x + Josh. 15.31.\x*, laseMekona lemizaneni yayo\x + Nani 21.25.\x*,
\v 29 laseEni-Rimoni\x + Josh. 15.32.\x*, laseZora\x + Josh. 15.33.\x*, laseJarimuthi\x + Josh. 10.3.\x*,
\v 30 iZanowa\x + 3.13.\x*, iAdulamu\x + 1 Sam. 22.1.\x* lemizana yayo, iLakishi lamasimu ayo\x + Josh. 10.3.\x*, iAzeka\x + Josh. 10.10.\x* lemizana yayo\x + Nani 21.25.\x*. Basebemisa inkamba kusukela eBherishebha\x + Josh. 15.26,27,28.\x* kusiya esihotsheni seHinomu\x + Josh. 15.8.\x*.
\v 31 Labantwana bakoBhenjamini kusukela eGeba babeseMikimashi, leAyija\x + 7.32. Josh. 7.2. 8.9. Ezra 2.28.\x*, leBhetheli\x + 7.32. Josh. 7.2. 8.9. Ezra 2.28.\x* lemizana yayo\x + Nani 21.25.\x*,
\v 32 iAnathothi\x + Josh. 21.18.\x*, iNobi\x + 1 Sam. 21.1.\x*, iAnaniya,
\v 33 iHazori\x + Josh. 15.23,25. 2 Sam. 13.23.\x*, iRama\x + Josh. 18.25.\x*, iGithayimi\x + 2 Sam. 4.3.\x*,
\v 34 iHadidi\x + Ezra 2.33.\x*, iZeboyimi\x + 1 Sam. 13.18.\x*, iNebalati,
\v 35 iLodi\x + 1 Lan. 8.12.\x*, leOno\x + 1 Lan. 8.12.\x*, isigodi sezingcitshi\x + 1 Lan. 4.14.\x*.
\v 36 LakumaLevi kwakulezigaba zakoJuda \add lo\add*Bhenjamini\x + 12.27.\x*.
